author: The Associated Press
title: Inslee takes Trump to task for fomenting 'insubordination'
description: OLYMPIA, Wash. (AP) — Washington Gov. Jay Inslee again blasted President Donald Trump’s call to “liberate” parts of the country from state stay-at-home and other orders designed to combat the spread of the coronavirus, saying Sunday that Trump is fomenting…
content: The governor said Trumps statements were doubly frustrating and exhibited such a schizophrenia because they contradict guidelines on reopening state economies issued last week by the White House. Those guidelines leave it to the states to determine when to re… [+1502 chars]
